77
00:02:31,851 --> 00:02:33,229
"JC's Rockin' Birthday Jam."

78
00:02:33,383 --> 00:02:34,688
Brick's in it.
He's gonna be a wise man.

79
00:02:34,814 --> 00:02:38,352
But get this--
I... am making the cookies!

80
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:39,532
Aah!

81
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:41,206
Brick's gonna be in a <i>play?</i>

82
