It could be his thing.

97
00:03:10,089 --> 00:03:12,832
All those actors
in Hollywood are weird, right?

98
00:03:12,948 --> 00:03:13,970
Brick's weird.

99
00:03:14,125 --> 00:03:15,339
Yeah, he's definitely that.

100
00:03:15,707 --> 00:03:17,814
I don't know, Mike.
I think he might surprise us.

101
00:03:17,997 --> 00:03:20,165
- He won't.
- Wh--

102
00:03:20,773 --> 00:03:22,433
(Lights clack,
dog barking in distance)

103
00:03:22,551 --> 00:03:23,502
Where are you going?

104
00:03:23,621 --> 00:03:25,536
I told Rusty I'd help him
move some furniture.

105
00:03:25,675 --> 00:03:26,910
Yeah, 'cause everyone knows

106
00:03:27,024 --> 00:03:29,552
