is when it's dark out.

107
00:03:29,676 --> 00:03:31,076
I guess some friend of his

108
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:32,979
is giving him some old stuff
from his place,

109
00:03:33,097 --> 00:03:34,610
and he wants
the stuff moved out

110
00:03:34,727 --> 00:03:35,937
before he gets back into town.

111
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,729
This is ridiculous.
Seriously, Mike,

112
00:03:37,855 --> 00:03:39,407
what is wrong
with your brother?

113
