The "what's <i>not</i> wrong with him"
list is shorter.

114
00:03:42,629 --> 00:03:45,486
(Sighs)
Hey, Axl. I was thinking.

115
00:03:45,674 --> 00:03:46,607
What if this year,

116
00:03:46,764 --> 00:03:48,131
