tonight, Mike.

140
00:04:44,210 --> 00:04:45,145
Uh, somethin' wrong?

141
00:04:45,247 --> 00:04:46,681
Yeah, there's
something wrong, Rusty.

142
00:04:46,799 --> 00:04:48,342
I didn't know we were gonna be
moving all this furniture

143
