into my garage.

144
00:04:49,687 --> 00:04:51,314
Oh. Well, we haven't
moved our old stuff

145
00:04:51,450 --> 00:04:53,917
out of Marlene's yet.
I guess I forgot to tell ya.

146
00:04:54,030 --> 00:04:54,900
Mm.

147
00:04:55,121 --> 00:04:57,010
Okay, let's get
this garage door down.

148
00:04:57,123 --> 00:04:58,692
We wouldn't want people
knowing it's here.

149
00:04:58,799 --> 00:04:59,759
Hang on.

150
00:04:59,892 --> 00:05:02,249
Why wouldn't we want people
knowing it's here?

151
00:05:02,442 --> 00:05:03,902
This is your stuff, right?

152
00:05:04,030 --> 00:05:06,685
Oh. Yes.
I won it fair and square.

153
00:05:06,852 --> 00:05:08,333
What do you mean, you "won it"?

154
00:05:08,449 --> 00:05:09,677
Well, uh, me
and a bunch of the guys

155
00:05:09,832 --> 00:05:12,435
were playin' poker,
and I called acey deucey.

156
00:05:12,562 --> 00:05:14,570
Sure, I had a lot
of corn nuts in my mouth,

157
00:05:14,698 --> 00:05:16,049
but everybody heard me.

158
00:05:16,171 --> 00:05:18,332
Uh-huh. And if you asked
the guy we took it from,

159
00:05:18,452 --> 00:05:20,062
- what would he say?
- Oh, he'd say we stole it.

160
00:05:20,275 --> 00:05:22,391
And what would the other people
at the table say?

161
00:05:22,506 --> 00:05:23,858
Well, they'd probably
side with him.

162
00:05:23,971 --> 00:05:25,378
You know how cops
stick together.

163
00:05:26,261 --> 00:05:27,963
You telling me
we broke into a cop's house

164
00:05:28,101 --> 00:05:29,864
and stole his furniture?
Are you nuts?!

165
00:05:29,988 --> 00:05:31,951
Now look, any jury
that plays poker

166
00:05:32,239 --> 00:05:33,204
would side with me.

167
00:05:33,368 --> 00:05:35,522
I'm not keeping this stuff
in my garage, Rusty.

168
00:05:35,622 --> 00:05:36,732
It's going back now.

169
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:38,688
Oh, I can't now.
I gotta get the truck back

170
00:05:38,810 --> 00:05:40,720
before the guy who owns it
finds out it's missing.

171
00:05:40,825 --> 00:05:42,156
So you stole a truck, too?

172
00:05:42,293 --> 00:05:44,807
Well, he'd say that,
but he owes me.

173
00:05:44,953 --> 00:05:47,408
You know those guys
that take and take

174
00:05:47,525 --> 00:05:49,187
and never give back?

175
00:05:49,366 --> 00:05:51,468
Yeah. I think I do.

176
