Okay, I figure 20 cast members,
2 parents each.

177
00:06:03,159 --> 00:06:05,197
Siblings, 1.5 grandparents,

178
00:06:05,338 --> 00:06:06,713
crew members, church people,

179
00:06:06,856 --> 00:06:08,780
5% accidental crumblage.

180
00:06:08,909 --> 00:06:11,262
Okay, I am going to need...

181
00:06:11,516 --> 00:06:14,269
1,200 cookies. Ha ha!

182
00:06:15,257 --> 00:06:16,123
Sue, quilt.

183
00:06:16,237 --> 00:06:17,397
Aah! Sorry.

184
00:06:18,044 --> 00:06:20,512
(Door squeaks) Ugh.

185
00:06:23,266 --> 00:06:27,111
So... guess who got hired
at JJ Macky's?

186
00:06:27,220 --> 00:06:28,979
Why do people say "guess who"?
I know it's you.

187
00:06:29,098 --> 00:06:30,995
(Sighs) Can't you just
have fun with this?

188
00:06:31,135 --> 00:06:33,265
Look, they're hiring
extra help for the holidays.

189
00:06:33,388 --> 00:06:34,130
And the best part is,

190
00:06:34,251 --> 00:06:36,443
