♪ hey, hey, hey,
we gotta follow that star ♪

197
00:06:48,977 --> 00:06:50,790
♪ I know it looks like
it's really far ♪

198
00:06:50,915 --> 00:06:52,234
♪ but we gotta, gotta,
gotta, gotta ♪

199
00:06:52,348 --> 00:06:54,750
♪ follow that star, yeah! ♪

200
