buy their presents,

224
00:07:43,814 --> 00:07:46,000
- and then quit.
- What?

225
00:07:46,153 --> 00:07:47,310
Well, that's not me.

226
00:07:47,493 --> 00:07:49,443
If anything,
I wanna be a lifer.

227
00:07:49,614 --> 00:07:51,274
Uh-huh. There's nothing
I would like better

228
00:07:51,402 --> 00:07:54,358
than to just grow old
and die here.

229
00:07:54,667 --> 00:07:55,588
Well, if you do,

230
00:07:55,743 --> 00:07:57,524
we all sign a vest, frame it,

231
00:07:57,643 --> 00:07:59,116
and give it to your family.

232
00:07:59,594 --> 00:08:01,335
(Exhales)

233
