<i>I was on my way over</i>
<i>to get that furniture,</i>

238
00:08:12,908 --> 00:08:16,764
<i>but then I realized</i>
<i>I don't have any shoes.</i>

239
00:08:16,943 --> 00:08:18,682
<i>I'll keep you posted.</i>
<i>(Beep)</i>

240
00:08:18,785 --> 00:08:20,916
<i>Hey, Mike.</i>
<i>Good news. I got the truck.</i>

241
00:08:21,047 --> 00:08:23,379
<i>But then dad asked me to</i>
<i>help him pick up folding chairs</i>

242
00:08:23,508 --> 00:08:25,413
