244
00:08:29,036 --> 00:08:30,386
<i>I'll keep you posted.</i>
<i>(Beep)</i>

245
00:08:30,573 --> 00:08:32,434
<i>Hey, sorry I haven't called</i>
<i>in a few days.</i>

246
00:08:32,549 --> 00:08:35,249
<i>I lost your number,</i>
